  "time_ut": 1662355692,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc4\u0db6\u0dba\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd3 \u2019\u2019\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u2019\u2019 \u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d82\u0dc1\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Ministry of Foreign Affairs is responsible for maintaining \"friendship\" at the oar of the fertilizer ship",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forest Conservation, Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera said that it has been decided to entrust the preparation of a process to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs in order to deal with the problem of the Chinese fertilizer ship in a way that does not damage the friendship between the two countries.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture said that President Ranil Wickremesinghe's position in the matter regarding this fertilizer ship is to resolve the issue in such a way that the friendly relations between the two countries are not damaged.",
        "Speaking to the media regarding the special report issued by the Auditor General, the minister said this regarding the fertilizer ship bought by China's Qingdao Sea Win Biotech Institute.",
        "The Minister said that whoever was involved in the transaction related to this fertilizer ship, the burden of the 6.9 million dollars paid for the ship was ultimately borne by the people of the country."
      ],
